name: Doug Britton
quote: Startup Shell is a powerful asset for student entrepreneurs who want to develop muscles that aren't covered in any courses: professionalism, tenacity and networking.

name: Holly DeArmond
quote: Startup Shell provides a space and sense of community where student entrepreneurs can go and meet like-minded students who are committed to solving problems and launching businesses.

name: Eric Schwartz
quote: For a student-founded incubator, that's a lot of impressive accomplishments.

name: Kristin Pryor
quote: [Startup Shell] is home to a lot of really interesting student-led projects
